"1. Basic Pulse Playback" = "1. 基本脉搏播放";
"- Tap START on the Home screen to open the pulse screen." = "- 在首页点击 START 打开脉搏界面。";
"- Tap START again to begin black-screen pulse playback." = "- 再次点击 START，在黑屏中开始脉搏播放。";
"- Double tap the black screen to stop playback." = "- 双击黑屏可停止播放。";
"- Double tap when leaving pulse measurement playback." = "- 退出脉搏测量播放时也请双击。";
"2. Pulse Controls" = "2. 脉搏控制";
"- Pulse slider: sets regular pulse rate in bpm." = "- 脉搏滑块：设置规则心率（bpm）。";
"- Pulse (Weak): lowers haptic intensity to simulate weaker palpation." = "- 脉搏（微弱）：降低触觉强度以模拟较弱触诊。";
"3. Arrhythmia Modes" = "3. 心律失常模式";
"- Arrhythmia (PVC): simulates premature beats with compensatory pause." = "- 心律失常（PVC）：模拟早搏及代偿间歇。";
"- Arrhythmia (AF): simulates irregularly irregular rhythm." = "- 心律失常（AF）：模拟完全不规则节律。";
"- Only one arrhythmia mode can be ON at a time." = "- 同一时间只能开启一种心律失常模式。";
"4. AF Sliders (Settings Sheet)" = "4. AF 滑块（设置面板）";
"- Mean Rate (bpm): average ventricular rate target during AF." = "- 平均心率（bpm）：AF 时平均心室率目标。";
"- Irregularity (%): variability of beat-to-beat interval." = "- 不规则度（%）：相邻心搏间期变化程度。";
"  - Lower value: rhythm feels closer to regular." = "  - 数值越低：节律越接近规则。";
"  - Higher value: rhythm feels more chaotic." = "  - 数值越高：节律越混乱。";
"5. Set Data Workflow" = "5. 数据集流程";
"- Open Set Data from Home bottom navigation." = "- 在首页底部导航打开 Set Data。";
"- Tap + to build a new SET profile." = "- 点击 + 新建 SET 配置。";
"- Tap SET to save." = "- 点击 SET 保存。";
"- Tap a row to play that saved pattern on black screen." = "- 点击列表行可在黑屏中播放该已保存模式。";
"- Swipe left on a row to delete it." = "- 左滑列表行可删除。";
